    <item>
      <title>欧盟监督机构称法国和意大利必须抓紧时间修复预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/france-and-italy-must-seize-day-to-fix-budgets-eu-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟咨询监督机构敦促欧盟负债最多的国家控制支出，并削减官员认为过度扩张的赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/france-and-italy-must-seize-day-to-fix-budgets-eu-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:09:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本届最高法院的赢家：特朗普、华尔街和保守派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/supreme-court-s-term-recap-trump-wins-big-regulatory-landscape-altered</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院的保守主义革命又迎来了一次变革性的任期，共和党任命的绝对多数削减了监管者的权力，消除了唐纳德·特朗普竞选总统过程中的法律阴云，并为未来的重磅大案奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/supreme-court-s-term-recap-trump-wins-big-regulatory-landscape-altered</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚总统鲁托在抗议声中阻止公务员年度加薪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/kenya-s-ruto-blocks-state-employee-annual-pay-rise-amid-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托要求国家财政部审查本月开始生效的公务员年度工资增长计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/kenya-s-ruto-blocks-state-employee-annual-pay-rise-amid-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普利兹克敦促拜登在辩论不佳后向美国人发表讲话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/pritzker-urges-biden-to-address-americans-after-debate-debacle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊利诺伊州州长 J.B. 普利兹克敦促总统乔·拜登向全国发表讲话，解释他的战略，并消除人们的担忧，此前他在与前总统唐纳德·特朗普的辩论中表现糟糕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/pritzker-urges-biden-to-address-americans-after-debate-debacle</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:41:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称乌克兰正在讨论向欧盟输送阿塞拜疆天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-discussing-transit-of-azeri-gas-to-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，乌克兰正在就从阿塞拜疆向欧盟输送天然气进行谈判，以寻求保持其作为过境国的角色并帮助西方邻国确保能源安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-discussing-transit-of-azeri-gas-to-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基挑战特朗普披露结束战争的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/zelenskiy-challenges-trump-to-reveal-plans-for-quick-end-to-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，特朗普应该提出尽快结束与俄罗斯战争的计划，并警告称任何提议都必须避免侵犯国家主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/zelenskiy-challenges-trump-to-reveal-plans-for-quick-end-to-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及内阁改组推动新兴市场债券市场涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/egypt-names-cabinet-of-economists-executives-to-boost-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及任命一位投资者友好的前世界银行经济学家担任财政部长，同时任命企业高管和前银行家担任其他重要职位，以期该国摆脱几十年来最严重的经济危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/egypt-names-cabinet-of-economists-executives-to-boost-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普封口费案为何陷入法律困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/why-scotus-immunity-ruling-put-trump-s-hush-money-conviction-in-limbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于最高法院于 7 月 1 日就总统豁免权作出了具有里程碑意义的裁决，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 因伪造商业记录掩盖性丑闻而被控 34 项重罪，但这一判决目前仍悬而未决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/why-scotus-immunity-ruling-put-trump-s-hush-money-conviction-in-limbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 21:38:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国阻止向中国国有船舶制造商出售燃气轮机机组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/germany-blocks-man-s-sale-of-gas-turbine-unit-to-chinese-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国政府出于国家安全考虑，阻止了德国曼恩能源解决方案公司（MAN Energy Solutions SE）将其旗下的燃气轮机业务出售给一家中国国有船舶制造公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/germany-blocks-man-s-sale-of-gas-turbine-unit-to-chinese-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:36:15 GMT</pubDate>
